{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
    "name": "SkillForge API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for SkillForge — a full-stack placement-focused student dashboard.\n\n## Setup\n1. Set the `baseUrl` variable to your backend URL (default: `http://localhost:8080`)\n2. Run the **Login** request first — it auto-saves the JWT token to `authToken`\n3. All protected endpoints use `{{authToken}}` automatically\n\n## Authentication Flow\n1. Register a new account via `POST /api/auth/register`\n2. Login via `POST /api/auth/login` → token is saved to `authToken` variable\n3. All subsequent requests use the token via `Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "authToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
